	<h1 class="title">音乐节这个生意，钱都被几个公司赚了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Ben Sisario</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-01 08:38:04 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9054/medium/9054.jpg?1436688678" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


